  section
    p.
      This is a project to build a Mandelbrot set renderer in JavaScript and HTML5 (okay, actually 
      <a href="http://livescript.net/">LiveScript</a> and <a href="http://jade-lang.com/">Jade</a>, but the end
      product is the same either way). <a href="mandelbrot.html">Click this link</a> to see it in action!

